39:58.997 --> 40:02.100
It was great. We had fun.

40:02.133 --> 40:04.102
-We can see that.
-You're practically glowing.

40:04.135 --> 40:05.537
A whole new you.

40:05.571 --> 40:07.739
I'm starting to feel
like myself again.

